Set up the structure
 what do we need to do? What does the computer se/display and what does the computer think?

1. Display the start / play button
2. When the user clicks on the start / play button, the first question is displayed.
3. When the user clicks on one of the answers, the next question appears.
    At the same time, add to the score count if the answer is correct.
4. If the user clicks the answer for the last question,
    the total score is displayed to the user.
    The result page will say "Thank you for completing my quiz!" "Your score is: __"
    with the total score displayed after "is: "
5. In the final result page you will have a "Try again?" button for starting the quiz over
    with the score being reset to 0.
